Safeway Inc And Exxon Mobil Corp Partner To Offer New Fuel Rewards Program
Wednesday, 30 Jan 2013 09:12am EST
Safeway Inc and Exxon Mobil Corp announced that they have teamed up to provide Safeway shoppers a new way to save at the pump. Safeway shoppers and ExxonMobil customers can earn Reward Points for products purchased at Safeway stores in the Mid-Atlantic region and redeem their Reward Points at participating Exxon or Mobil locations. This new loyalty program will help maximize the value and savings provided to Safeway and ExxonMobil customers through the combination of convenience and rewards.Â 
